@Comment:	what is vampier faivrite candy a secker [= last two words are written upside down on the page like in a joke book; there are several erasures and cross outs on the page]
@Comment:	Chi balances tablet on raised knees. Chi feels very uncomfortable and doesn't want to write. EXP , INV2 and Mot suggest numerous ideas , but Chi refuses to write anything. After approximately seven and a half minutes of fussing (including a discussion about their avian pet , Larry Bird) , Chi suddenly decides to write a joke (INV2's suggestion) and does a good job; Chi complains <Ma how come you always make me sound it out>; Mot replies <because I used to be a teacher>
@Situation:	at first Chi chooses to sit at the table , but Mot points to the couch and Chi returns to sit next to her.
